ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Overall I very much enjoyed the course, particularly doing the readings and working on the final paper, and I would definitely recommend the course, and the graduate sessions were interesting and useful. My main difficulty with the course is that during the class itself it felt very much directed towards, and directed for the benefit of, undergraduate learning. It was difficult to engage in graduate-level discussion of the interesting issues raised by the readings during the class itself.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
